# Security Utilities Guidance

- Keep encryption/decryption primitives server-only and isolated from UI imports.
- Use authenticated encryption patterns and random IVs/nonces per secret payload.
- Include key versioning hooks to support future rotation without data loss.
- Normalize token creation and verification with explicit expiry and scope checks.
- Ensure helper functions fail closed: invalid input should deny access by default.
